{"tid":1358054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地政經常縱容霸佔官地人士，應否施壓地政立即檢控何君堯？","createTime":"2019-07-24T00:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T00:39:54.000Z","uid":271270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"16b819f49a1be3ff5f63164b427f9c5dbc3c2eed","tid":1358054,"uid":271270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:38:05.000Z","msg":"引一段建制媒體觀點先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01觀點/118896/01觀點-屢屢縱容霸佔官地-地政總署有責難辭\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E%2F118896%2F01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E-%E5%B1%A2%E5%B1%A2%E7%B8%B1%E5%AE%B9%E9%9C%B8%E4%BD%94%E5%AE%98%E5%9C%B0-%E5%9C%B0%E6%94%BF%E7%B8%BD%E7%BD%B2%E6%9C%89%E8%B2%AC%E9%9B%A3%E8%BE%AD&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1SUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=760373be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01觀點/118896/01觀點-屢屢縱容霸佔官地-地政總署有責難辭</a><br />\n<br />\n「至於非法佔地，現時地政總署一般只要求涉事者拆除建築，還原土地原來的面貌，觀乎 2015 年 2 月起的《佔用政府土地條文》，首次佔用且被定罪者可罰款達 50 萬、監禁 6 個月，再犯者更可被罰 100 萬元及監禁 6 個月。可以說，公眾過去對地政總署的監管視若無睹，原因就是署方對犯法者不施以重罰。往後若署方遇到同類事件，須考慮及早提堂處理，以收殺一儆百之效。」<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n地政總署應該立即檢控何君堯，罰款監禁+勒令佢立即起返佢兩副骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8371148d414772bacebda70fb0613c2a7dbf04e2","tid":1358054,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:39:54.000Z","msg":"元朗手足有野講 727去唔去都入黎睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}